cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

This paper is about improving end-to-end speech recognition using RNN-T models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. The paper also discusses optimization of the training algorithm, which falls under the category of cs.SD (Software Engineering). The use of machine learning models and optimization techniques suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the advantages of RNN-T models for online streaming, which could fall under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
